Trainers

Prebon, Ignatius and Spears arrived back at the base. When Ignatius 
flew down low, Prebon lifted Spears off his back.

"You were wondeful! I can't believe how good you are!"

Meanwhile, Hammer arrvied at K9's position.

"There is no way you are following us, Maximal! DIE!"

Hammer opened a panel on his arm, and pulled out a grenade. He 
pressed the button and laucnhed it. He got his plasma rifle ready 
just incase this bot survived the blast.
______________________________________________________________________
Vulois

Vulois stepped in front of Child.

"Hold on Child. You have just learned this power. Too much use before 
training could cause an overload, killing yourself in the process."
Vulois than went into a fighting stance an looked at AngelNemesis.

"I, on the other hand, have been training my power for months, and 
know my limitations. Now Nemesis, watch the power of good triumph 
over evil!"

Vuloic concentrated, and formed an energy sword in his hand. It 
glowed with all the light of the heavens.

"Good-bye, Nemesis."

Vulois charged, repeadidly slashing with the sword.
______________________________________________________________________
Brix/Fliq

Brix nodded.

"All right. You can count on us." He than turned to the rest of the 
group. 

"All right guys. Let's give Ramulus room to think. Let's install the 
new computer boards so we can maybe get this thing up and running."

Brix and Fliq picked up Computer boards and carried them inside.
